data.name: LEG URINE BAGS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- Polyethylene (PE) Body
- PVC and DEHP-FREE PVC Tubing
- Polypropylene (PP) Clamps, Caps and Hangers

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- PVC and DEHP-FREE PVC
- Customized Printing
- T-Cross / Screw Outlets
- Elastic Holders
- Ridged Universal Connector
- Needle and Needle free Sampling Port
- With and Without Soft Non Woven Backside

## PERFORMANCE
- 2 Litters Capacity
- Non-Flow Return Valve
- Air vented Constant Airflow
- Clear, flexible, kink-resistant inlet PVC tubing
- Highly Transparent
